# Docs last updated for version

v1.18.0

## How to use this file

When updating docs next time, run:

```bash
# Get all changes since docs were last updated
git log v1.18.0..HEAD --oneline
```

Then update this file to the new version after the docs PR is merged.

## What was covered in this update

- Execution profiles: definition format, auto-discovery, per-instance resolution, control composition
- Automation triggers and trigger bindings (TriggerBinding documents)
- CI environment auto-detection (`--from-ci` for GitHub Actions, GitLab CI, Buildkite)
- Stack override policies (StackOverridePolicy documents)
- Convention-over-configuration auto-discovery for all stack resources (profiles/, triggers/, policies/)
- Composition-scoped profiles (`compositions/<type>/profiles/*.yaml`)
- `orun fetch` command for downloading OCI composition packages locally
- Job identity fields: `uid`, `displayName`, `checkName`
- New `orun plan` flags: `--profile`, `--trigger`, `--from-ci`, `--event-file`
- Environment execution settings (`execution.profile`, `execution.profiles`, `execution.controlOverrides`)
- Rich subscription format (per-environment profile overrides in component manifests)
- New concept pages: profiles.md, automation.md
- New CLI page: orun-fetch.md
- Updated: intent-model, stacks, orun-plan, orun (command map), plan-schema, configuration, environment-variables, intro, sidebars, README
